<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَتَّاوَى الإِمامِ النَّوَوَيِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">المُسمَّاةِ:</span> <span class="c1">"بالمَسَائِل المنْثورَةِ"</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ترتيبُ:</span> تلميذه الشيخ عَلَاء الدِّين بن العَطّار<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">تحقِيق وتعلِيق:</span> محمَّد الحجَّار<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قوبِلَت عَلى نسخَةٍ خطيّةٍ قديمَةٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>دَارُ البشائرِ الإسلاميَّة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>